+++ b/tick_flow_full/orderflow_services/runbook_exec_health_freeze_integrity_v1.md
@@ -0,0 +1,18 @@
+# ExecHealth Freeze Integrity (v1)
+
+Purpose: detect control/state deletion, unsigned thaw, or missing signed ack-event.
+
+Key checks:
+- pending ack nonce exists after autoguard freeze
+- manual thaw must emit signed `manual_ack_thaw` event
+- control/state disappearance without valid ack-event is a tamper violation
+
+Primary metrics:
+- `exec_health_freeze_integrity_violation{kind=...}`
+- `exec_health_freeze_integrity_pending_ack`
+- `exec_health_freeze_integrity_valid_ack_event_present`
+
+Operator flow:
+1. `status` to read the current pending nonce.
+2. `thaw --nonce <pending_nonce> --operator ... --reason ... --ticket ...`
+3. Verify exporter shows `valid_ack_event_present=1` and `violation{kind="none"}=1`.
